ZH: 我们应该依靠自己的能力实现梦想。
EN: We should rely on our own abilities to achieve our dreams.

ZH: 她依靠母亲的支持完成学业。
EN: She relied on her mother's support to complete her education.

ZH: 这个公司依靠创新来保持竞争力。
EN: This company relies on innovation to maintain its competitiveness.

ZH: 他依靠计划和组织能力成功完成项目。
EN: He succeeded in completing the project by relying on planning and organizational skills.

ZH: 孩子们依靠老师的指导学到了很多知识。
EN: The children learned a lot by relying on the guidance of their teachers.

ZH: 这家餐厅依靠优质的食材赢得了很多忠实的顾客。
EN: This restaurant has won many loyal customers by relying on high-quality ingredients.

ZH: 老人依靠子女的照顾过上了幸福的晚年生活。
EN: The elderly person is living a happy life in their old age by relying on the care of their children.

ZH: 我们不能仅仅依靠运气来获得成功。
EN: We cannot solely rely on luck to achieve success.

ZH: 这个国家依靠出口创造了许多就业机会。
EN: This country has created many job opportunities by relying on exports.

ZH: 他们要依靠合作来解决问题。
EN: They need to rely on cooperation to solve the problem.

ZH: 我们应该依靠自己而不是依赖他人。
EN: We should rely on ourselves instead of relying on others.

ZH: 这个团队依靠团结和合作来完成任务。
EN: This team relies on unity and cooperation to accomplish the task.

ZH: 她能否成功依靠于她的努力和毅力。
EN: Whether she can succeed depends on her efforts and perseverance.

ZH: 我们需要依靠科学来解决现代问题。
EN: We need to rely on science to solve modern problems.

ZH: 这个国家依靠农业发展经济。
EN: This country relies on agriculture to develop its economy.

ZH: 学生们应该依靠自己的努力来取得好成绩。
EN: Students should rely on their own efforts to achieve good grades.

ZH: 他们依靠团队合作顺利地完成了任务。
EN: They successfully completed the task by relying on teamwork.

ZH: 我们应该依靠专业知识来解决问题。
EN: We should rely on professional knowledge to solve problems.

ZH: 老板依靠自己的经验判断市场形势。
EN: The boss relies on their own experience to judge the market situation.

ZH: 这个计划依靠资金支持才能实施。
EN: This plan can only be implemented with financial support.
